name: "Ichi-go Ich-e" by potentialight.art
description: @potentialight Hicetnunc Exclusive ✦ 2020 px x 2020 px 33/33 edition.  ⦿ "Ichi-go Ich-e” is about always becoming. Always arriving in the present moment.
